1. PM-133 / P1: openHelpDrawer() at lines 1655-1658 opens the help drawer unconditionally. It does not guard on currentTableId or redirect to setShowTableConfirmSheet(true), so hall users without a verified table still enter the help drawer and hit the in-drawer error path instead of the table-code sheet.
