5. PM-135 / P2: openHelpDrawer() does not reset helpQuickSent, sendingCardId, showOtherForm, or helpComment before reopening. Because only closeHelpDrawer() resets them, a fast reopen can show stale success or stale form state.
   Proposed fix: reset `setHelpQuickSent(false)`, `setSendingCardId(null)`, `setShowOtherForm(false)`, and `setHelpComment('"'')"'` before `setIsHelpModalOpen(true)` and update the dependency array accordingly.
