+2. [P2] "Другое" textarea is still CSS-hidden instead of conditionally rendered — [`pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:3767`](/C:/Users/ASUS/Dev/Menu%20AI%20Cowork/menuapp-code-review/pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx#L3767) keeps the form mounted with `overflow-hidden transition-all ... max-h-0 opacity-0`, so PM-134(a) is not implemented. FIX: replace the collapsible block with `{showOtherForm && (...)}`.
+3. [P2] "Другое" textarea lacks `autoFocus` — [`pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:3769`](/C:/Users/ASUS/Dev/Menu%20AI%20Cowork/menuapp-code-review/pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx#L3769) mounts the textarea without `autoFocus`, so PM-134(b) is still missing. FIX: add `autoFocus` to the conditionally rendered textarea.
